<item>
            <title>[HBASE-11756] Some assignment notifications are not triggered</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11756</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In AssignmentManager, notifications are triggered when regions are opened/closed. However, notifications are not always triggered. For example, when a server is dead, regions are closed implicitly, and no notifications are triggered.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is it a better place to trigger such events in RegionStates?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
